  <facts><![CDATA[<h3>What do our Santa Breaks include?</h3>
<ul>
<li>A visit to Santa’s Elves Hideaway, an exclusive excursion plus private meeting with Santa</li>
<li>Arctic thermal suits and snow boots for all adults &amp; children (3yrs +)</li>
<li>Choice of accommodations in Muonio, Levi and Ylläs </li>
<li>A special Festive Feast full of festivities including fun and games</li>
</ul>
<h3><strong>Good to know</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Currency:</strong> Euro</p>
<p><strong>Fly into:</strong> Kittilä</p>
<p><strong>Fly from:</strong> London Gatwick, Manchester, Bristol </p>
<p><strong>Flight time:</strong> approx. 3 hours</p>
<p><strong>Transfers by coach:</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li>Levi - approx. 20 minutes</li>
<li>Ylläs - approx. 55 minutes - 1¼ hours</li>
<li>Muonio - approx. 1 - 1¼ hours</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Price match promise –</strong> <span>If you're yet to book, and you find your Inghams Lapland holiday cheaper elsewhere, we’ll price match it</span></p>]]></facts>
